Notes from our Swab Cab roll out:

1. LGU Malabon provided medical teams for 3 swab cabs;

2. BHERTs in 5 brgys covered identified who needed to be swabbed after house-to-house assessment, took charge of orientation and contact tracing;

3. 3 teams from OVP were in testing areas; https://t.co/82yqmMkxz6

Updates from the ground:

1. Nag iimprovise na po sila ng balsa, nahihirapan sila kasi madami daw po talaga nag rqst na ma rescue;

2. Yung sa Linao East yung Coast Guard at PNP Maritime wt rubber boats lng nakakapasok kasi lagpas tao yung tubig.

